      </li>
      <li>
        <span class="check-list__icon text-highlight" aria-hidden="true">{{> icon-check-circle}}</span>
        <span>Movement and positioning tools you can use from pregnancy all the way through to pushing</span>
      </li>
      <li>
        <span class="check-list__icon text-highlight" aria-hidden="true">{{> icon-check-circle}}</span>
        <span>Clarity on your birth values and preferences and the language to advocate for them</span>
      </li>
      <li>
        <span class="check-list__icon text-highlight" aria-hidden="true">{{> icon-check-circle}}</span>
        <span>The ability to navigate the maternity system with confidence</span>
      </li>
      <li>
        <span class="check-list__icon text-highlight" aria-hidden="true">{{> icon-check-circle}}</span>
        <span>Moments of genuine connection with your birth partner around one of the biggest experiences of your lives</span>
